item.description: welcome to Introduction of Data Science at Mercyhurst University HI! Welcome to my blog about the intro to data science class directed by Dr. Redmond at Mercyhurst University. We will be using R studio, SQL, and ggplot to identify visualization. If you do not know about any of these tools, feel free to look at my website with examples.https://gkenda87.github.io/website/ Also, if you have any questions, feel free to contact me with my email or social media posted in the sidebar.
